sources.title: Kansas City Confidential (Film-Noir, 1952) John Payne, Lee Van Cleef | One double-cross too many.
sources.description:
A down-on-his-luck ex-GI finds himself framed for an armored car robbery. When he’s finally released for lack of evidence–after having been beaten up and tortured by the police–he sets out to discover who set him up, and why. The trail leads him into Mexico and a web of hired killers and corrupt cops.

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/jvVkjTzAvYA

Director: Phil Karlson 
Writers: George Bruce, Harry Essex 
Stars: John Payne, Coleen Gray, Preston Foster, Neville Brand & Lee Van Cleef
Genre:  Classics, Cult Film, Crime, Drama, Film-Noir
